---

<div id="devtools-warning" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:99999;background:#0a0a0a;color:#f5f5f5;font-family:serif;">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:100vh;text-align:center;padding:2rem;">
    <div>
      <h1 style="font-size:4rem;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#c9a87c;">Nice try! ðŸ‘€</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;opacity:0.7;">This is a protected demo template.</p>
